Do steps in this order to keep the build green after each step:

1. Update `build.bat` (drop SDL, add XInput) and verify it still compiles.
2. Copy `pixel_art_shader.hlsl`.
3. Extend `platform.h` and `vario.h` (adds fields — backward compatible).
