5. Replace `windows_file_io.h` and merge `windows_gpu_transfer.h` / `windows_renderer_setup.h`.
6. Copy `shared_input.cpp` and `shared_renderer.cpp`.
7. Replace `windows_main.cpp` (the main work — build and test here).
8. Verify 3D rendering still works (run the game, check 3D scene).
9. Verify 2D rendering works (add a test 2D sprite call from game code).
